tal, ambient to punchier beats like Dubstep, DNB and ultimately Mid-Tempo and Riddim. NexDrak creates soundscapes that transport listeners to strange futuristic realms, hopefully this man doesn't know what hope means.\\\"}]\\nc:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"With each release and performance, Nex continues to push the boundaries of music or at least tries to, exploring the intersection of technology and human emotion through sound.\\\"}]\\nd:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"relative aspect-square select-none pointer-events-none\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L15\\\",null,{\\\"src\\\":\\\"/img/others/xayah.jpg\\\",\\\"alt\\\":\\\"NexDrak Artist Photo\\\",\\\"fill\\\":true,\\\"className\\\":\\\"object-cover rounded-xl\\\",\\\"draggable\\\":false,\\\"priority\\\":true}]}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"e:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 rounded-xl p-8 mb-20\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"MUSICAL JOURNEY\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"space-y-8\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"md:w-1/4 flex flex-col items-center md:items-end\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-white font-bold text-xl\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"2014\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"h-full w-px bg-white/30 my-2 hidden md:block\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"md:w-3/4 bg-black/30 p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/10\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h3\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-bold mb-2\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Beginnings \\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-gray-300\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Start creating remixes and edits of several Vocaloid (CircusP) songs like “iNFeCTioN” and “Thunder Storm”. Previously adopted the name PowerDark but this was changed for being too little “imposing” in his opinion. That same year he released his first single on SoundCloud under the name “Sky Bridge”.\\\"}]]}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"md:w-1/4 flex flex-col items-center md:items-end\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-white font-bold text-xl\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"2015\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"h-full w-px bg-white/30 my-2 hidden md:block\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"md:w-3/4 bg-black/30 p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/10\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h3\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-bold mb-2\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Start on YouTube\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-gray-300\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"In this year he created his music channel and resubmitted many of his songs on this channel and formally adopted the name “NexDrak”, in this year he released “Loop Lovely” and “DownFall” laying the foundations of his musical genre, but let's not forget some very disastrous tracks that we prefer not to mention.\\\"}]]}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"md:w-1/4 flex flex-col items-center md:items-end\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-white font-bold text-xl\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"2017\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"h-full w-px bg-white/30 my-2 hidden md:block\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"md:w-3/4 bg-black/30 p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/10\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h3\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-bold mb-2\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Beat Basis\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-gray-300\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"In this year he managed to consolidate himself as an emotive principle with tracks like “Your Smile” and “Time Out”.\\\"}]]}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"md:w-1/4 flex flex-col items-center md:items-end\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-white font-bold text-xl\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"2018\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"h-full w-px bg-white/30 my-2 hidden md:block\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"md:w-3/4 bg-black/30 p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/10\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h3\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-bold mb-2\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Growth\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-gray-300\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Thanks to his singles like “Even to Dream” and “Akai” he positioned himself as a reference in the London Dubstep community.\\\"}]]}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"md:w-1/4 flex flex-col items-center md:items-end\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-white font-bold text-xl\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"2020\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"h-full w-px bg-white/30 my-2 hidden md:block\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"md:w-3/4 bg-black/30 p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/10\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h3\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-bold mb-2\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Live Showcase\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-gray-300\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"In 2020 he made his first presentation in CDMX, with the support of The Chainsmokers, this presentation was not as disastrous as he expected, this same year he made his second event in the bar “Pan y Circo”, creating a more solid audience. This same year he released his first EP called “Your Lie” a little different to his established style.\\\"}]]}]]}],\\\"$L16\\\"]}]]}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"f:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-20\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"order-2 md:order-1\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"LIVE EXPERIENCE\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"space-y-4 text-gray-300\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"A NexDrak live performance is more than just music: it's a fully immersive sensory journey.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Each show is unique, with custom-designed visuals that respond in real time to the music, creating a symbiotic relationship between sound and sight.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"symbiotic relationship between sound and sight that envelops the audience in creative vision, we know your career as a computer scientist helps.\\\"}]]}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"relative aspect-video order-1 md:order-2\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L15\\\",null,{\\\"src\\\":\\\"img/live_experience.png\\\",\\\"alt\\\":\\\"NexDrak Live Performance\\\",\\\"fill\\\":true,\\\"className\\\":\\\"object-cover rounded-xl\\\",\\\"draggable\\\":false}]}]]}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"10:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-center mb-16\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-2xl font-bold mb-6\\\",\\\"children\\\":\